Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\b1}The Faceless Ones: Episode 2{\b\b}\N{\b1\b1}无面一族: 第二集{\b\b}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,【中文翻译/时间轴】巴蛮子sz
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定从来没见过他们? 他们说认识你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're quite sure you've never met these men?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They say they know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.85,0:01:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们不可能认识我, 这是我第一次来英国!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But they can't know me.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is my first visit to England!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Polly, 是我们啊, 是我和博士!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But Polly, it's us, me and the Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可否告诉我们你的名字?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Would you mind telling us your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫 Michelle Leuppi, 来自苏黎世\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I am Michelle Leuppi from Zurich.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你有护照吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You have a passport?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有, 当然有, 这里\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, of course. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我做错什么了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Have I done something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哦没有, 我觉得这里没有什么你需要担心的, 小姐\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh no, I don't suppose there's anything\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}for you to worry about, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以问问你来英国做什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}May I just ask what you're doing in England?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来工作的. 看, 这是我的工作许可\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I have come here to work.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Look, here is my work permit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 是, 完全没问题. 谢谢你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, yes, that's quite in order. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那里学的这么好的英语?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Where did you learn such excellent English?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个英语家庭教师\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I had an English governess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你介意告诉这是怎么一回事吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Would you mind telling me what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么需要你操心的, 小姐, 一切都没问题\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Nothing that need concern you, miss,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}everything's perfectly in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你可以从这边走了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now if you'd just like to go through there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Polly, 等等!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Polly, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你先等等, 年轻人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Just a minute young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但她是我们的朋友啊——她还看见了那场谋杀!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But she's a friend of ours - and she saw the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩得在这里等着, 直到警司来了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're going to wait here\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}until the Superintendent of police arrives
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,现在明白了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}now understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啊, 你要告诉他那具死尸的事情, 非常明智\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ah, you're going to tell him\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}about the dead body, very sensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不, 我要告诉他你们的事情\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No. I am going to tell him about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,给我接 Reynolds 警司\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Put me through to Superintendent Reynolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie, 我觉得我们在这里不是太受欢迎\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jamie, I don't think we're very welcome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,等我说跑的时候, 就跑\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}When I say run, we run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你好, 警司, 我是总指挥\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hello Super, Commandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我这里有两个非法入境者\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've got a couple of illegal entrants here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对...出入境五号柜台\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes... Immigration Desk Number Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,跑!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,总指挥!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Commandant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,情况有变, 他们刚刚逃跑了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Situation changed. They've just made a run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我把他们详细描述给你...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll give you their description...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快! 他要窒息了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Quick! He's suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你们晚了20分钟\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You were twenty minutes late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Meadows, 是航空控制塔台的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Meadows - Air Traffic Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很好! 他可能对我们有用\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Good! He may be useful to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还在搜寻我们, 博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They're still hunting for us, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 我们必须躲着他们, 直到我们能自圆其说\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes. We'll have to keep out of their way\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}until we can prove our story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,本来有一个很好的机会证明的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}A fine chance we have of doing that -
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但Polly居然开玩笑说她不认识我们!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}with Polly kidding on she doesn't know us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得 Polly 是在开玩笑\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't think Polly was kidding on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上, 我觉得那不是 Polly\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}In fact, I don't think that was Polly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是, 就是 Polly! 你都看见了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Of course, it was Polly! You saw her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你不应该相信所有你看见的事情, Jamie\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You don't want to believe everything you see, Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了, 博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All clear, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,博士!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie, 那个机库的名字叫什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jamie, what was the name of that hangar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Polly 说过变色龙什么的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Polly said Chameleon something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊, 变色龙观光游\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, Chameleon Tours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是变色龙青年观光游的广告\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}An advertisement for Chameleon Youth Tours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻人的廉价旅游, 为18-25岁量身定做\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}"Budget Tours for young people\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}between the ages of eighteen and twenty five. "
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,廉价是什么意思?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What do they mean by budget?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,费用少, 便宜!  这可能是诱饵\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Inexpensive, cheap! This could be the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道变色龙是什么吗, Jamie?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you know what a chameleon is, Jamie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,只是个名字吧, 我估计?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's just a name, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是一种小动物的名字, 一种蜥蜴\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It is the name of a small animal, a lizard
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,它能改变它身体的颜色, 以与周边环境融为一体\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}that can change its colour\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to merge with its background.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但这个名字一样可用在人身上\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But it's a name that could equally\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}be applied to people as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人为了自己的目的会改变自己的特性\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}People who change their personalities\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to suit their own ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,廉价旅游...为18-25岁年轻人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Budget Tours... young people\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}between the ages of eighteen and twenty-five
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是了, 这里肯定有些奇怪的事情\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh yes, there's something strange going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 博士! Jamie!   - Ben! 你没事吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Doctor! Jamie!  - Ben! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:05:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯, 我没事 - 那还真松了一口气\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Yeah, I'm okay.  - Well that's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩怎么了? Polly 又在哪儿?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What happened to you two and where's Polly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能在这里说\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We can't talk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,得找个地方躲起来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We've got to find somewhere to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,躲那些找我们要护照的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Something about passports.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我正好有个地方, 快来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've got the very place. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他没事吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Is he all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看看吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,读第一行\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Read the first line!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,发声控制器\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Vocal control.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,试试那个\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,H...​ X... O... A...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}H... X... O... A...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,都搞定了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是George Meadows\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}My name is George Meadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我在航空控制塔台工作, 盖特威克机场\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I work at Air Traffic Control, Gatwick Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你住在哪里?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,希尔维亚大街10号\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Number Ten, Sylvia Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,10号?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Number Ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在上周之前, 我们住在34号\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Until last week, We lived at Number Thirty-Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我前一段太忙, 还没有将这个变化通知人事部门\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've been too busy to tell\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}the Personnel Department of the change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快看! 那是Polly!  - 是的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Look! There's Polly!  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你看她在给谁干活!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Look who she's working for!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 变色龙观光旅游  - 是的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Chameleon Tours.  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,把这交给我吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pol​ly\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Polly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,请走开\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Please go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看, 你肯定出事了, Polly\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now, something has happened to you, Polly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我期望你尽力回忆一下, 我们离开机库之前那些\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I want you to try to remember\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}up to the time we left the hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,想想, Polly. 当时我们三个在机库\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now think, Polly.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There were three of us in the hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我们看了点东西, 是什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You were showing us something. Now what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说, 我不知道你在说些什么\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I tell you, I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,机库, Polly, 变色龙的机库\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The hangar, Polly, The Chameleon Hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你还看见了是谁干的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You said you'd seen the man who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么也没看见, 我猜你是疯了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I didn't see anything. I think you're mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我看见有人被枪杀了, 我会去找警察的...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}If I'd seen anyone shot,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'd have gone to the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有人被枪杀了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Anyone shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我是说被谋害了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I... I mean murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没说有人被枪杀或者被谋害了, Polly\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I didn't say anyone was shot, or murdered, Polly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了, 能不能别烦我\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Look, please, will you just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她这是怎么了, 博士?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What's happened to her, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道, 但我打算查明白\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't know. But I mean to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快来, 我们找一个可以说话的地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Come on, let's find that place where we can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,到这里面来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Come in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来正要跟你交待这个任务的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I was going to brief you for this assignment,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在没什么必要了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but there isn't any purpose, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是我搞砸了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I have failed, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,环境对你不利\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Circumstances are against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我会安排你搭下一航班离开\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll make arrangements for you\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to leave on the next flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,回基地?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Back to base?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人怎么办? 他很执着\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What about that man? He's very persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Don't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有好多方法对付这样的人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We have ways of dealing with such people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定你没有见过他, 先生?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Are you sure you haven't seen him, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我相当确定\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm quite sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, Jean, 这位是 Crossland 督察\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh Jean, this is Detective Inspector Crossland.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,尽你所能给他一些协助\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Give him any help you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那我先告辞了?   - 好的, 当然, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- If you'll excuse me? - Yes, of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,督察, 有什么可以帮你的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well now Inspector, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 我想首先我需要一张通行证\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, I think I'll need a pass for a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那很容易安排\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well that's easily arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有, 本来我是要在这里跟我的一个同事碰面的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, I was supposed to meet a colleague of mine here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一位叫 Gascoigne 的督察  - 怎么了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- a Detective Inspector Gascoigne.   - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 他正在调查一个人口失踪案\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, he was investigating a missing person
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,事关你们的一趟租赁航班\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}off one of your charter flights.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但奇怪的是, 他没出现\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The funny thing is, he hasn't shown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Crossland 督察...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Detective-Inspector Crossland...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我能问问你这次的公务是...?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What shall I say your business is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:11:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,调查变色龙青年旅游\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Investigation into Chameleon Youth Tours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一台给你们拍照片的机器\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's a machine that takes your photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,照片?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 喏, 你看你得...  - 别 Ben, 现在别\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Well, you see you've got...  - No Ben, not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我想不通的是, 这女孩试图假扮成 Polly, 但是...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What puzzles me is this girl\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}pretending to be Polly, yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,某种程度上来说, 她又是 Polly\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}yet in a way, she is Polly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得她会是被洗脑了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you think she's been brainwashed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不, 时间不够\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, not in the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不管她遭遇了什么, 都在短短几分钟之内. 小心!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Whatever happened to her happened to her\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}in a few minutes. Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, Jamie, 我们必须得去多找一些变色龙观光游的情况\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ben, Jamie, we've got to find out\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}more about Chameleon Youth Tours,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不过问题是, 我们没法自由行动\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but the trouble is, we're not free to move around
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,当局还在找我们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}with the authorities looking for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对了, 他们并没有在找我\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, they're not looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那倒是, 你可以去机库调查\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, that's true. You could investigate the hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就交给我吧. 那你们呢?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Leave it to me. Now what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去找总指挥\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm going back to the Commandant
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,尽力说服他这里有个凶手\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and try and convince him that there's a murderer abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那, 我跟 Ben 一起去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well I'll go with Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不, Jamie, 我要你原路返回\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, Jamie, I want you to find your way back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,到变色龙柜台去, 盯着点 Polly\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to the Chameleon kiosk and keep an eye on Polly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}再次通知飞往日内瓦的 BR129 航班{\i}\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Further call for flight BR129 to Geneva...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}现在开始在19号登机口B通道登机{\i}\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}now boarding through channel B at gate number 19.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:12:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是你负责吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh! Err, are you in charge here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 有什么可以帮你的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ah, yes. Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有, 我叫 Samatha Briggs, 我从利物浦来的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes. I... I'm Samantha Briggs\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and I've come down from Liverpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 真的啊\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是关于我弟弟的事情, 他叫 Brian Brigg\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's about my brother, Brian Briggs -
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他来参加你们的一个观光旅游, 但他现在不见了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He went on one of your tours,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and now he's disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起, 我没明白\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm sorry, I don't follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哎, 这真的很简单\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, it's really very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你们送他去的那个酒店, 我试图去查它的电话号码\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I tried to get the telephone number\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}of the hotel you sent him to,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但接线员说没有这样一个地方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and the operator said there was no such place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那, 接线员肯定搞错了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, the operator must have been mistaken then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,于是...我就联系了警方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}So... I got in touch with the police
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们说 Brian 不在罗马的任何一个酒店里\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and they said that Brian\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}wasn't staying at any hotel in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 也许他改主意了, 然后跑去了别的旅游团\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, um, perhaps he changed his mind\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and decided to go on a different tour then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那你看看这个怎么说?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well what about this then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Brian 寄来的明信片, 从罗马寄来的!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}A post-card from Brian, posted in Rome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 这看起来有点奇怪, 是不?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, that does seem odd, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,呃, 我帮你查查你看可以吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Erm, would you like me to make some enquiries for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那你觉得我大老远从利物浦跑来是为了什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, what do you think\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've come all the way down from Liverpool for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你都把情况告诉警方了, 为什么还自己跑来?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well - since you've put the matter\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}with the police, why have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,警察, 他们说每周都有好几打人失踪\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Police. They said that dozens of people\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}go missing every week
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而他们没有足够的人全部展开调查\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and they haven't got the men to go chasing after them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了. 你说你弟弟的名字叫什么来着?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I see. What did you say your brother's name was?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Brian Briggs. 你期望我给你拼出来么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Brian Briggs. Would you like me to spell it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要, 谢谢你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That won't be necessary, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看我能查出什么来, 如果你愿意等的话\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll see what I can find out, if you don't mind waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Blade 机长在吗不?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Is Captain Blade there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不在\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须得跟他通话, 很紧急\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, I must speak with him - urgently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,关于一个失踪乘客的事情\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Enquiries about a missing passenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让他跟你联系, 不会很久的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll tell him to contact you. He shouldn't be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我要找的那位先生现在不在\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The gentleman I wanted to speak with wasn't available,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他们找他去了. 你愿意等一会儿吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}they're trying to find him. Do you want to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没有其它事情可做啊, 对吧?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, I've got nothing else to do, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在那边\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'll be over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 该死!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么事吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Is anything the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,自以为是的东西!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Stuck up thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么?   - 不是说你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What?  - Not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女的, 她一点也不在乎\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That girl! She just couldn't care less.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,找你弟弟的事情\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}About finding your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是  - 我不小心听到了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Yes.   - I couldn't help overhearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他是不是出了什么事?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you think something's happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 这个问题, 我说不好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, that's just it, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, Brian 倒是能自己照顾自己, 不过还是...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, Brian can take care of himself all right, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 但愿你是对的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Aye, well I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你什么意思?   - 我也许可以帮到你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What d'you mean?  - I might just be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但目前我不能告诉任何情况\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I can't tell you anything at the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但稍后我带你见我一个朋友\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but later I'd like you to meet a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信他知道怎样处理最好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm sure he'll know what's best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有位绅士要见你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There's a gentleman to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他说了是什么事吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Did he say what about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哦说了, 是一具死尸的事\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well yes. It's about a dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,带他进来吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你可以进来吗?   - 谢谢你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Would you come in, please?  - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,啊, 总指挥, 很高兴再次见到你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ah, Commandant. How nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,请接机场警方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Airport Police please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,至少听听我有什么要说的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}At least hear what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经听够你那些废话了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've heard all I want to from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思, 他们都占线? 我是总指挥\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What do you mean, they're engaged.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is the Commandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你打算跟警方通话, 赶紧告诉他们...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}If you're going to speak to the police,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}then tell them that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,机场现在有事发生, 可能会危及很多人的性命\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}there's something happening in this airport\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}that may endanger human lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是警方吗? 我是总指挥\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hello police? Commandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请你们能不能立即派几个人过来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Would you send a couple of men down here at once please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我马上就要被捕了, 能不能提个最后的请求?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Since I'm obviously about to be arrested\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}may I make one last request?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就听我说一分钟\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Listen to me for just one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一秒钟也不听\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Not for one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经听够了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've heard all I want to hear about
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,烧焦的纤维、射线枪、消失的尸体. . .\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}burnt fibres, ray guns, disappearing bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但变色龙观光团的机库的确有过一具死尸!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But there was a dead body in the Chameleon Tours hangar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才是说“变色龙观光团”?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Did you say "Chameleon Tours"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么, 你知道它一些情况?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Why, do you know something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道, 但这位 Crossland 督察想要了解...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, but the Inspector Crossland wanted to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, Jean, 我来处理吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right, Jean. I'll handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,啊, 把这个人带走, 锁起来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ah, take this man away, put him under lock and key
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,把他一直关在那儿!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and keep him there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,再走近一步, 我就把你们炸成碎片!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}One step nearer and I'll blow you all to smithereens!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,接着!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 去追!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right, after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,都相当清楚了吧, 是不?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That's quite clear, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道怎么跟她说了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You know what to tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦你甩掉这个女孩, 就把柜台关了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}As soon as you've got rid of the girl, close the kiosk
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,登上下一班飞机\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and get on the next flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Briggs 小姐\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Miss Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在, 你查到什么了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes. Have you found anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,呃, 是的, 我查到了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Err, well yes, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不过恐怕没有太大的帮助\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But I'm afraid it doesn't help very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你弟弟的确是搭上了我们去罗马的航班\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Your brother definitely did get on our flight to Rome,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但他下飞机之后做了什么, 我就没法告诉你了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but what he did when he got off the plane,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I couldn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,啊, 如果你不能, 谁能?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, if you can't, who can?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Briggs 小姐, 我们每周都要跟上千乘客打交道\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Miss Briggs, We're dealing with\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}thousands of passengers every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不可能跟踪每一个人的行踪\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We can't keep track of every single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是你, 就会回到利物浦去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}If I were you, I'd go back to Liverpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信你弟弟最终会露面的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm sure your brother will turn up eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,现在, 什么别的事情的话, 我得关闭柜台了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now, if you'll excuse me, I have to close this kiosk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你什么事都没干\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Thanks for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这事还真是有意思  - 为什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- There's something funny going on here.   - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我弟弟不见了, 而那家伙完全漠不关心\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}My brother's vanished, and that lot just couldn't care less.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你好, 这个机场的总负责人叫什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hello? What's the name of the man\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}who's in charge of this airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,总指挥?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The Commandant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好, 你能帮我接到他的办公室吗, 拜托?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Right, well look, can you put me\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}through to his office, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 那接航空控制塔台\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right, then Air Traffic Control
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想跟我的一个朋友通话\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but I want to speak to a friend of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在应该跟总指挥在一起\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}who should be with the Commandant right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,博士, 我期望你见见这位年轻女士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor, I'd like you to meet this young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什么年轻女士? Polly 在哪儿?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What young lady? Where's Polly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她还在里面\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}She's still inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,啊, 我一分钟就回来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ah, I shan't be a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Po​lly...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Polly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但你为什么不听他的? 都是真的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But why wouldn't you listen to him? It's all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在在变色龙机库, 而我刚刚发...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm in the Chameleon Hangar now and I've just f...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ben​!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, 你能听到我吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ben, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, 你能听到我吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ben, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, 你没事吧, 能听到我说话吗? Ben!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ben, are you all right, can you hear me? Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ben​!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, 你能听到我吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ben, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,屏幕上那个博士的一个朋友\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}A friend of that Doctor on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他看到那里发生的事情了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Did he see what happened in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定看到了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He must have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那他肯定会过来, 我们最好给他做点准备\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Then he'll be coming here.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We'd better be prepared for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,首先, 处理掉尸体\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}First, dispose of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫 Brian Briggs\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}His name's Brian Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,据说是一周前来到这里的, 度假\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Supposed to have come through here\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}about a week ago, on holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,每周都有上千人来到这里\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Thousands of people come through here a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 只是试试机会\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Aye, well it was just a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还记得那个人吗?   - 是的, 我记得他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Do you remember that man?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Oh yes, I remember him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他有通行证, 但我想不起他的名字了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He had a pass. But I can't remember his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我的一个同事, Gascoigne 督察\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He's a colleague of mine,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Detective Inspector Gascoigne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他什么时候回来的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now when did he come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法告诉你, 太多面孔了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I couldn't tell you. There are so many faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上这里有点状况, 他可能那时候溜过去了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There was a bit of bother this morning,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}he could have slipped through then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的状况?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What sort of bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有两个没有护照的人...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Two people without passports...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...叨叨着说什么在一个机库里面发现了一具尸体\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}...who told some sort of story about a body in a hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 具体什么情况?   - 啊, 只是场闹剧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What happened?  - Ah, it was all a hoax.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这两人跑掉了, 机场警察现在还在四处找他们!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}These two men they ran away.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The airport police are still looking for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你能向我描述一下他们的样子吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Can you describe them to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一个外表有点邋遢, 中等个子, 穿着一件长外衣\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}One was a scruffy-looking man,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}medium-height, wearing a frock-coat,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个是个苏格兰小伙子, 穿着苏格兰草裙\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}the other was a Scots boy dressed in a kilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 应该不难找到\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, shouldn't be too hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿, 你觉得我们应该去找你的朋友不?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hey, you think we should go after your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经走了10分钟了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He's been gone about ten minutes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不用, 他说了半个小时. 现在, 我们按他说的做\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, he said half an hour.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now, we'll do what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿, 他可真是个怪人, 不是吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hey, he is a right weirdy, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是! 我期望我能有他的脑子\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No! I wish I had his brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你倒是挺正常的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're all right as you are.
